# Local vehicle template asset store (GH-003/004 dev stopgap; real blob storage
# is GH-005). Written at runtime by the admin upload + the seed loader.
.vehicle-assets/

# License-restricted vehicle template TEST inputs (ProVehicleOutlines .ai files
# + their derived SVG/PDF outputs). PVO EULA forbids derivative works for
# unlicensed catalog use — these files exist locally for prototype testing only
# and MUST NOT be committed. Real catalog seeds come from licensed/owned sources
# per spec §5.3.
apps/web/public/vehicle-templates/test-only/

